{
  "stem": "4078.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they would alert-- they-- they had what they called these stirrup pump things, which were these pump things that you just stood on with water at the back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you pumped and you tried to put them out, and sort of allay the-- the burning until the fire department came.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he did that on a volunteer basis, and so he was gone two nights a week.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was all very, very exciting, until it apparently got to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got quite ill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I became quite ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, I have to go back and say this lady who had this-- she had these two large homes, these two large houses on this very nice street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One she had as a boarding house that she supplied food for the people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the house where we lived in, she supp-- she had rooms with little kitchenettes or burners, and that's what we had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "However, during the blitz, everybody would congregate-- all the tenants from the two houses would congregate in this lady's room in her house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we would sing, and we would joke, and it was funny, and it was great.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we would listen to Vera Lynn on the radio, and we would listen to Alvar Lidell, who was the BBC news announcer, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] announcing all about the war.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a lot, a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We really enjoy-- and I enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, being up late, not having any sense of, well, now it's bedtime and now you have to do homework and now you have to do that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing structured, and I loved it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every night.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
